{"tid":1498001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"元朗西鐵站襲擊事件：兩白衣男子被控暴動罪提堂　案件押後獲准保釋","createTime":"2019-08-23T08:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T08:24:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"609aa4d1c550b84b0acf0061327302874b0a6ad0","tid":1498001,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476333-20190823.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476333-20190823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=9d1f43b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1476333-20190823.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bfb9294a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1476333-20190823.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗西鐵站襲擊事件，兩名男子各被控一項暴動罪，下午在粉嶺裁判法院提堂。兩人暫時毋須答辯，案件押後至10月25日再訊。控方反對兩人保釋，裁判官經考慮後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">容許兩人保釋</span></span></strong>，條件包括現金3萬元、交出旅遊證件及宵禁令、又不得出現在元朗西鐵站及附近50米範圍。<br />\n<br />\n54歲的王志榮及48歲的黃英傑，分別報稱運輸工人及其他職業，各被控一項暴動罪，涉嫌違反《公安條例》，被指在上月21日，在西鐵元朗站內連同其他不知名人士參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n控方在庭上讀出案情，表示上月20日晚上約10時40分，約50名白衣人在元朗站先與一班黑衣人口角，兩邊都有使用暴力，包括掟水樽及用水喉射水。及後包括兩名被告用籐條、木棍等向人施襲，被告王志榮有用垃圾桶蓋施襲，及後大批白衣人再到月台及車廂施暴，造成極大恐慌，包括有一名男子下跪求饒，而被告王志榮被閉路電視影到出現在白衣人附近。至於另一被告黃英傑無戴口罩，及後兩名被告都被通緝，警方翌日拘捕王志榮，並在他家中搜出褲及鞋，與案發當日吻合。至於黃英傑，就在本月3日在羅湖準備離港時被捕，他曾承認當日曾到元朗站及有與人口角。<br />\n<br />\n控方形容案情嚴重，施暴行為有組織及有預謀，施暴維持約30分鐘。控方說，最少24名受害人身體有不同程度受傷，包括骨折。"},{"pid":"10e21dd1794453cafd03a9c5f64ae0f94c241eee","tid":1498001,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"西瓜達人起訴未？"},{"pid":"7e7ee267c2f05c9d13e29bef7055d1749b7432dc","tid":1498001,"uid":84308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"警方已向 824「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」觀塘遊行集會活動發出不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n路線為：駿業街遊樂場&gt;駿業街&gt;海濱道&gt;順業街&gt;偉業街&gt;常怡道&gt;宏照道&gt;零碳天地外<br />\n<br />\n詳情將會稍後透過KT tg channel 發放：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">「燃點香港&middot;全民覺醒」</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">五大訴求、缺一不可</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">智能燈柱、侵犯私穩</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>日期：24/8/2019<br />\n時間：1300集會、1330遊行、1600解散<br />\n集會地點：駿業街遊樂場<br />\n遊行起點：駿業街遊樂場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公海： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824discuss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824discuss&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=55735378\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824discuss</a><br />\n<br />\n資料發佈： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824info&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=6d0c304c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824info</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣： <a href=\"http://t.me/kt824promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkt824promo&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=3ecf878f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/kt824promo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qbBYwct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbBYwct.jpg&h=cabbffda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a9a77fc24cacd9f2f5436420f124c56829f6010","tid":1498001,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10e21dd1794453cafd03a9c5f64ae0f94c241eee","tid":1498001,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"西瓜達人起訴未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"未<br />\n<br />\n仲食緊西瓜"}]}